  "scopeAndContentNote": "This film demonstrates the steps needed to gather information for the NBC-1 nuclear report that is used to determine nuclear yield and make fallout predictions. Stress is placed on the observer's location; flash-to-bang time; cloud width; and azimuth to attack to determine the location of ground zero and nuclear yield.",
